{"tid":2082304,"cid":18,"subCid":6,"title":"佛教話，人類追求永生只會帶來苦難。基督教話，人類必須懂得追求永生，不能沉醉今生。","createTime":"2020-06-28T02:41:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-04T14:00:35.000Z","uid":149978,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"2a51f663dff6cb0c295f661100e5d2d30c7ea2ac","tid":2082304,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T02:41:43.000Z","msg":"佛教四諦 - 苦集諦：<strong>人的苦難來自永恆的生存欲，</strong>因為生死流轉永無寧日，終日擔憂。之所以有這種種痛苦，是因為有產生痛苦的根源，主要是貪、嗔、癡。<br />\n<br />\n基督教：人類犯了罪便有了死亡，唯有悔改信靠神可得永生上天堂。人類應以追求永生為人生主要目標。"},{"pid":"a25fe343fc811c774dbb228a242b51185bfa6d7d","tid":2082304,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T02:41:55.000Z","msg":"大家會信邊樣多？"},{"pid":"53b8a9417dffe304a957cca4ad16fad8e87009f6","tid":2082304,"uid":57237,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T02:42:58.000Z","msg":"佛教"},{"pid":"cf64ce31cdd1691ac43d01bb91d1da9f48ca12d5","tid":2082304,"uid":201031,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T02:45:28.000Z","msg":"人生存就係受難<br />\n但又唔畀自殺自我解脫"},{"pid":"906102de829db27891fc9c8e9a46ef02a14cb90b","tid":2082304,"uid":1654,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"2a51f663dff6cb0c295f661100e5d2d30c7ea2ac","tid":2082304,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T02:41:43.000Z","msg":"佛教四諦 - 苦集諦：<strong>人的苦難來自永恆的生存欲，</strong>因為生死流轉永無寧日，終日擔憂。之所以有這種種痛苦，是因為有產生痛苦的根源，主要是貪、嗔、癡。<br />\n<br />\n基督教：人類犯了罪便有了死亡，唯有悔改信靠神可得永生上天堂。人類應以追求永生為人生主要目標。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T02:45:39.000Z","msg":"佛教講緊要成佛、要超脫輪迴喎，靠自己（小乘）或他人（大乘）去脫離人世既苦難"},{"pid":"8cf2c93f08b94e7b089d4c301575d1a46d07edae","tid":2082304,"uid":191145,"like":11,"dislike":3,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T02:46:28.000Z","msg":"佛教講無限輪迴 如果拉長睇都係「永生」 <br />\n只係業力牽引 導致用不同角色、身分係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">現世中</span></span>去進行<br />\n以要擺脫輪迴為目標 <br />\n<br />\n基督所講係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">死後</span></span>上天堂 得永生 <br />\n<br />\n講緊兩個概念<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4341804ed6a243258681957d12159d360e8fd219","tid":2082304,"uid":145928,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T02:52:28.000Z","msg":"有衝突嗎？"},{"pid":"aa8dda5e615537586cb00068ed4db726be459845","tid":2082304,"uid":277374,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T03:11:22.000Z","msg":"只要有欲望，仍然會有煩惱，所以我唔相信上天堂係最完美嘅終點。"},{"pid":"b72ff64fb14bdf74837cd227239a94e536551c80","tid":2082304,"uid":149978,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4341804ed6a243258681957d12159d360e8fd219","tid":2082304,"uid":145928,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T02:52:28.000Z","msg":"有衝突嗎？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T03:11:27.000Z","msg":"當然有"},{"pid":"93e1335dc92bfdbae15f321345184ab478f1b854","tid":2082304,"uid":149978,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aa8dda5e615537586cb00068ed4db726be459845","tid":2082304,"uid":277374,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T03:11:22.000Z","msg":"只要有欲望，仍然會有煩惱，所以我唔相信上天堂係最完美嘅終點。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T03:12:19.000Z","msg":"基督教話上左天堂，人類聽晒上聽指示。<br />\n而上帝的旨示就係要人類在天堂享受生活。"},{"pid":"5fb26f7c99dbfbd15c7d72c409b6079cc361fe6e","tid":2082304,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T03:12:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>只要有欲望，仍然會有煩惱，所以我唔相信上天堂係最完美嘅終點。</blockquote><br />\n基督教話上左天堂，人類聽晒上<strong>帝</strong>聽指示。<br />\n而上帝的旨示就係要人類在天堂享受生活。</blockquote>"},{"pid":"03b1606ae5a5dc649bead9607dec2f6e6d21bc82","tid":2082304,"uid":277374,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"93e1335dc92bfdbae15f321345184ab478f1b854","tid":2082304,"uid":149978,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aa8dda5e615537586cb00068ed4db726be459845","tid":2082304,"uid":277374,"like":1,"dislike":1,"